# Environment Variables for finjuice
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# ⚠️ Never commit .env to git!

# =============================================================================
# Dashboard AI Chat Configuration (Optional)
# =============================================================================

# Option 1: Claude Code CLI (Recommended)
# ----------------------------------------
# Install: brew install claude-code
# Authenticate: claude login
# Requires: Claude Pro or Team subscription
# No environment variable needed (uses OAuth browser flow)

# Option 2: OpenAI API (Alternative)
# -----------------------------------
# Get your API key from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Uncomment and set your key below:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# =============================================================================
# Data Directory Configuration (Optional)
# =============================================================================

# Override default data directory (default: ~/.finjuice)
# FINJUICE_DATA_DIR=/path/to/your/data

# =============================================================================
# Notes
# =============================================================================

# - AI chat will automatically use Claude if available, fallback to OpenAI
# - If neither is configured, AI chat will be disabled
# - See docs/setup/ai-cli-setup.md for detailed setup instructions
